WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:28.460
The rhythm tickles against my chest. I laugh lightly…

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:32.080
I want to become a blue jewel!

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:35.740
I want to be kept with great care…

00:00:35.980 --> 00:00:42.700
Words tickle against my ears. My heart’s beating faster and faster…

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:46.400
I didn’t even have time to tell my love fortune,

00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:50.140
Because you went and came along.

00:00:57.500 --> 00:01:03.940
Aah, I wonder why…?

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:22.760
It began, all of a sudden.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:26.580
I race ahead – tip-tap, ta-ta-ta.

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:29.860
I catch them on a whim:

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:33.740
The sounds of my footsteps – ta-ta-ta.

00:01:33.740 --> 00:01:37.100
I leave them to the wind that blew by.

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:40.800
I start to skip – lalala, ta-ta-ta

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:44.480
A love song is on my lips.

00:01:44.480 --> 00:01:56.380
I wonder if you’ll remember it…?

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:10.720
I hear that melody echoing about radiantly, and I smile shyly.

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:14.180
I can’t hate you, even after you make fun of me!

00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:17.740
Though, I sometimes end up freezing you over…

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:24.860
I wrote a letter for the first time, and you returned it: “I can’t read it.”

00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:28.620
I wonder if singing the songs I remember

00:02:28.620 --> 00:02:32.600
Is more like me?

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:46.260
Aah, I wonder what I should do…?

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:04.900
Today has begun again, as well.

00:03:04.900 --> 00:03:08.580
I chase after you – tip-tap, ta-ta-ta.

00:03:08.580 --> 00:03:11.980
I ambush you, and you’re surprised.

00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:15.740
I trip over – ouch!

00:03:15.740 --> 00:03:19.140
Any time, on a whim,

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:23.000
My busy heart spins around.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:26.300
I’ll teach that song of love to you!

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:30.300
Remember it always… always…

00:03:40.880 --> 00:03:52.780
Remember it always… always…

